  <body>

  <p>
A 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_screening_service">Screening Service</xref>
 is a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_service">SERVICE</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
A 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_screening_service">Screening Service</xref>
 is a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_service">SERVICE</xref>
 in which members of a defined population are offered a 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_screening_test">Screening Test</xref>
 to identify individuals who have risk factors or early stages of disease.  </p>
  <p>
For further information on the 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_screening_test">Screening Tests</xref>
 carried out by a 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_screening_service">Screening Service</xref>
, see the 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_department_of_health_and_social_care">Department of Health and Social Care</xref>
 part of the gov.uk website at: 
    <xref href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/nhs-population-screening-explained"
            scope="external"
            format="html">NHS population screening explained</xref>
.  </p>

